drm/i915: BDW Fix Halo PCI IDs marked as ULT.

BDW with PCI-IDs ended in "2" aren't ULT, but HALO.
Let's fix it and at least allow VGA to work on this units.

v2: forgot ammend and v1 doesn't compile

